headline: WTW to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year Earnings on February 4, 2025
summary: LONDON, Jan. 07, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- WTW (NASDAQ: WTW), a leading global advisory, broking and solutions company, will announce its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year 2024 on Tuesday, February 4, 2025 before the market opens.
